147
00:11:41,570 --> 00:11:42,460
Yes.

148
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:45,610
Please have a seat.

149
00:11:58,300 --> 00:12:00,040
I will now announce the sentence.

150
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:02,450
Case Number 2018.

151
00:12:02,450 --> 00:12:04,350
The 237th court.

152
00:12:04,350 --> 00:12:06,270
Defendant Lee Soon Cheol.

153
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:35,070
It is true that Lee Soon Cheol committed
assault in the ambulance and caused injury.

154
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:38,650
It is also true that a watch was damaged.

155
00:12:38,650 --> 00:12:41,350
The victim was inebriated, and if

156
00:12:41,350 --> 00:12:44,920
it was not an urgent enough situation
to justify a desperate intervention,

157
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:50,130
his actions for subduing a drunk
person can be viewed as extreme.

158
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,860
However.

159
00:12:52,860 --> 00:12:54,800
The entire process

160
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:57,990
was the action of an emergency responder

161
00:12:57,990 --> 00:13:00,560
committed to citizens' safety and well-being.

162
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:05,480
His good intentions of doing the best
he could, cannot be doubted.

163
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,010
The defendant

164
00:13:07,010 --> 00:13:10,400
experienced many cases
similar to this incident.

165
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:15,050
He was aware that his actions could
lead to legal repercussions.

166
00:13:15,050 --> 00:13:17,290
He still handled an emergency.

167
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:21,900
It was a brave act showing his
determination to save someone's life.

168
00:13:25,770 --> 00:13:27,380
The law...

169
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:29,860
cannot punish justified courage.

170
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:31,520
That justification

171
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:36,020
is based on a universal understanding
that a thankful act should be thanked.

172
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:37,200
Therefore,

173
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:42,860
Defendant Lee Soon Cheol,

174
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,760
