268
00:22:37,490 --> 00:22:39,320
Nice performance.

269
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:43,040
I made the accusation, so
I will be interrogated, too.

270
00:22:43,040 --> 00:22:48,660
Is it common for a judge to make
allegations to a prosecutor in court?

271
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:51,720
The chief prosecutor ordered
me ahead of time.

272
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:55,280
Let's be the messengers
of justice this time.

273
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:59,140
Get the arrest warrants, like clockwork.

274
00:22:59,140 --> 00:23:01,950
The media will help, too.

275
00:23:01,950 --> 00:23:05,310
Sunbae, get the star prosecutor
treatment this time.

276
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,020
A star?

277
00:23:09,250 --> 00:23:11,130
I have a headache.

278
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:14,600
In an organization, if you stick out
you get beaten with a hammer.

279
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:17,190
If you played a small role, sure.

280
00:23:17,190 --> 00:23:20,680
But once you are a top star,
you're untouchable.

281
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:22,460
Untouchable?

282
00:23:23,650 --> 00:23:25,200
Want to make a bet?

283
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:28,330
Whether you become a star or not?

284
00:23:28,330 --> 00:23:31,210
You be the star.

285
00:23:31,210 --> 00:23:35,650
Step over your father, Sang Cheol,
and live your best life.

286
00:23:35,650 --> 00:23:38,860
Tax evasion file on my father
will be sent to you soon.

287
00:23:38,860 --> 00:23:41,070
Please take good care of it.

288
00:23:43,270 --> 00:23:47,990
Your father is naively grabbing
onto Oh Sung for dear life.

289
00:23:49,910 --> 00:23:51,600
What about Han Soo Ho?

290
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,650
Headed somewhere nice?

291
00:23:53,650 --> 00:23:55,440
I don't know yet.

292
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:59,650
I looked into it, but it doesn't look
like a big firm or corporation.

293
00:23:59,650 --> 00:24:02,260
Of course.

294
00:24:02,260 --> 00:24:05,170
Troublemaker judge. Who would take him?

295
00:24:05,170 --> 00:24:09,340
He should just open a petty
private firm somewhere.

296
00:24:09,340 --> 00:24:10,900
Just watch.

297
00:24:10,900 --> 00:24:14,250
I will step all over that a**hole.

298
00:24:17,900 --> 00:24:19,800
[ Han Soo Ho ]

299
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:39,110
We prepared this for you.

300
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:43,090
Wherever you go, we hope
your wish comes true.

301
00:24:47,710 --> 00:24:48,750
Thank you.

302
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:51,380
I... after working here for over a year,

303
00:24:51,380 --> 00:24:54,430
only recently had a conversation with you.

304
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:56,000
Thank you, Your Honor.

305
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,210
Really?

306
00:24:57,210 --> 00:25:00,220
When we were getting signatures
for the employees' petition,

307
00:25:00,220 --> 00:25:04,590
you didn't sign, so I was sad
and resentful toward you.

308
00:25:04,590 --> 00:25:08,040
I had no idea you were such
a good person. I'm sorry.

309
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:09,100
Really?

310
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:10,900
Aigoo, the candle is burning.

311
00:25:10,900 --> 00:25:14,600
I told you guys not to make
a scene. Stop talking!

312
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:16,090
Blow it out, Your Honor.

313
00:25:16,090 --> 00:25:17,670
Have a good vacation.

314
00:25:17,670 --> 00:25:21,110
Let me know if any paperwork
is annoying to handle.

315
00:25:21,110 --> 00:25:26,550
I... from the first day you arrived
at this court and this office ...

316
00:25:29,330 --> 00:25:30,740
Geez!

317
00:25:32,710 --> 00:25:34,150
Hey.

318
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:38,010
Make a wish.

319
00:25:57,700 --> 00:26:05,850
♫ I'm wandering through
the darkness for a path ♫

320
00:26:05,850 --> 00:26:14,290
♫ This is where I will rest
my weary body, in my home ♫

321
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:16,900
Where are you going now?

322
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:22,480
To find a job?

323
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:26,710
♫ So I can take a deep breath ♫

324
00:26:26,710 --> 00:26:27,880
As a cook?

325
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:32,330
♫ Let me home, now ♫

326
00:26:34,290 --> 00:26:36,170
I'll come over later.

327
00:26:36,170 --> 00:26:38,170
I'll bring you a gift.

328
00:26:38,170 --> 00:26:39,870
I'll make you something delicious.

329
00:26:41,590 --> 00:26:46,860
♫ I won't break apart ♫

330
00:26:46,860 --> 00:26:54,210
♫ The memories that await me there ♫

331
00:26:54,210 --> 00:27:01,760
♫ Like a dream, the loneliness
pierces into me ♫

332
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:03,400
♫ I miss you, I can't fill up
the loneliness inside ♫
